question: Give me 5 pictures of rivers.
sparql: PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#> PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX yago: <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/> PREFIX y2geor: <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/resource/> PREFIX y2geoo: <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/> PREFIX strdf: <http://strdf.di.uoa.gr/ontology#> PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/> PREFIX da4dte: <http://ai.di.uoa.gr/da4dte/ontology/> PREFIX pnyqa: <http://pnyqa.di.uoa.gr/ontology/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> SELECT DISTINCT  ?c_picture_9 WHERE   { ?c_river_20  rdf:type          da4dte:river ;               geo:hasGeometry      ?cGeometry20 .     ?cGeometry20  geo:asWKT        ?cWKT20 .     ?c_picture_9  rdf:type         da4dte:Image ;               geo:hasGeometry      ?cGeometry9 .     ?cGeometry9  geo:asWKT         ?cWKT9 .     ?c_picture_9  da4dte:hasTimestamp  ?time .      ?c_river_20  geo:sfIntersects  ?c_picture_9   } LIMIT   5
